request, accept or make any payment for Listing Fees outside of the TravCP Platform or TravCP Payments. If you do so, you acknowledge and agree that you: (i) would be in breach of these Terms; (ii) accept all risks and responsibility for such payment, and (iii) hold TravCP harmless from any liability for such payment;
